, he rose to power with his disappearing sarcophagus act, but met his untimely end in an unfortunate goat accident. His tale is told in great detail on the back of his sarcophagus, which no one will ever see.","zh":"他以前是“腐王”的隔代堂兄，曾把自己藏在法老石棺中，这样他就是王了，但是很不幸他最后死于这场史上最冤屈的意外。他的经历被详细地刻在了石棺里面，尽管没人能够知晓。"},"DisplayOffset":{"x":15,"y":0},"DisplayScale":{"x":1,"y":1}}}}